{"word":"H6711 - צָחַק - tsâchaq - tsaw-khak' - Laugh - நகை","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>צָחַק"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>tsâchaq"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>tsaw-khak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Laugh / நகை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நகை, நகைத்திரு, சரசம்பண்ணு, விளையாடு, பரியாசம் பண்ணு, வேடிக்கைகாட்டு, விளையாடிக் கொண்டிரு."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to laugh, to mock, to play"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to laugh"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to jest"},{"paragraph":"2) to sport, to play, to make sport, to toy with, to make a toy of"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>laugh</i> outright (in merriment or scorn); by implication to <i>sport: - </i>laugh, mock, play, make sport."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3327 - יִצְחָק - Yitschâq - yits-khawk'/3327\">H3327</a>, <a href=\"#/H3446 - יִשְׂחָק - Yischâq - yis-khawk'/3446\">H3446</a>, <a href=\"#/H6711 - צָחַק - tsâchaq - tsaw-khak'/6711\">H6711</a>, <a href=\"#/H6712 - צְחֹק - tsᵉchôq - tsekh-oke'/6712\">H6712</a>"}]}